notes_for_type_of_tobacco: Rollies (Top-O-Matic Cigarette Rolling Machine) The Top-o-matic is one of the easiest RYO (roll your own) systems to use. Slip on your cigarette tube, fill the tobacco chamber based on your cigarette size. The tobacco chamber has two size options - king (84mm cigarettes are typically 3 - 3 1/4 inches in length)  or 100mm (simply known as 100's and are typically 3 3/4 - 4 inches in length). notes_co: 8/7/17- William C is unavailable to do CO test because he is currently homeless and Bay Cove employees are having trouble tracking him down--was advised to move on since it would be nearly impossible to track him. I started by going to the South Hampton Shelter in early October and was informed that he no longer resided there and was not allowed on the premises. I then went to the Fenwood Inn on multiple occasions, front desk said that they had seen him before and to check back later in the day, which we did four times. On the fourth time I was told that he actually hadn't been living there since September. His outreach workers have made no contact with him in months and he is basically of the map. There is no way for me to do the CO with him.
